Azure Databricks is an Apache Spark-based analytics service optimized for Azure.

Capabilities:

* Big data processing
* Machine learning
* Collaborative notebooks

For example, data scientists build ML models collaboratively in Databricks.

# Real-Life Use Case:
A real-life use case is fraud detection analytics.

# Real-Life Example:
Another example is recommendation engines.

Azure Databricks accelerates advanced analytics and AI workflows.
